_sText:
This is a port of this map: tr_outferno_co [Counter-Strike: Global Offensive]
You might find this usefull if you want to showcase your weapons or characters and need some kind of decorarions set. Like in CS:GO I guess.
My apologises for using Reshade and modified weapons from csgomod as I only really had those at my disposal.
And if you want to know more about this map, consider checking my Artstation post: Training Map in Classic Offensive Style with CS: GO Inferno/Canals assets
